description: Mashita means delicious, this truck is bringing the flavors of Korean cuisine in a delicious way. Specializing in homemade steamed buns and ssam (Korean Lettuce wraps) stuffed with tasteful slow cooked meats like a  customer favorite Bulgogi Korean BBQ. If you need to try something new head on over and have a refreshing experience with delicious options you are sure to enjoy. Mashita!
name: Mashita
